SELECT k AS video_id, seopath_l2 AS title, SUM(CASE WHEN vj>=1400 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS videoplays
FROM test.test_videos_historical
WHERE dateindex = CAST(date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_date), '%Y%m%d') AS VARCHAR)
GROUP BY k, seopath_l2
ORDER BY videoplays DESC
LIMIT 10
